  "detail": {
    "tagExpireTime": "1782093604152",
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1371671902013861888",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">您好，为适应业务发展和保障消费者体验，将针对<a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=923540006109319168\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》</a>进行修订。现进行规则公示，公示期：2026年6月15日- 2026年6月21日，规则预计于 2026年6月22日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">核心调整点：1、新增 【假大牌/假洋牌】违规条款；2、处置措施调整。</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">具体调整点如下：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 19.85pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增【假大牌/假洋牌】违规</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">假大牌/假洋牌违规：指商家打造一个没有真实品牌内涵的\"空壳品牌\"，通过高端包装和高价定价，让消费者误以为买到了大牌或洋牌，为此支付远超商品本身价值的溢价。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【处理措施】</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度一般： 违规商品下架，扣除违约金200元（M2档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度严重：违规商品下架，扣除违规商品近14天成交金额10%，最低100元，最高10,000元（M3档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度极其严重：违规商品下架，扣除违规商品近14天成交金额20%，最低300元，最高100,000元（M4档）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"color: #262626; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">5.2.5除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度一般： 违规商品下架或商品降流50%（7天），扣除违约金200元（M2档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度严重：违规商品下架或违规商品降流75%（7天），扣除违规商品近14天成交金额10%，最低100元，最高10,000元（M3档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度极其严重：违规商品下架或违规商品降流100%（7天），扣除违规商品近14天成交金额20%，最低300元，最高100,000元（M4档）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"color: #262626; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">5.2.5除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、<span style=\"color: #262626; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">扣除违约金-M6档（违规商品SKU近30天成交金额的10倍，最低30,000元）</span> 、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></span> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
